high_descs: Walk towards the black chairs on the other side of the room, then hang a right and walk over to the small wooden table to the left of the bed.
Pick up the rightmost phone off of the small wooden table.
Turn around and walk towards the wall, then hang a left and walk up to the middle of the end of the bed.
Place the phone onto the middle of the end of the bed.
Walk back over to the small round wooden table next to the bed.
Pick up the phone off of the wooden table.
Turn right and begin walking across the room, then hang a left and walk up to the end of the bed.
Place the phone on the bed to the left of the phone that's already there.
anns.task_desc: Move two phones from a table to the bed.

high_descs: Walk straight towards the 3 black chairs, turn right after the bet and go to the table next to the bed.
Pick up a phone on the table that is the closest to the bed.
Turn around and turn left after the bed, walk slightly and turn left to be at the other side of the bed.
Put the phone on the bed.
Go back to the table next to the bed.
Pick up another phone near the lamp on the table.
Go back to that other side of the bed again.
Put the phone next to the first phone on the bed.
anns.task_desc: Put 2 phone side by side on the side of a bed with no lap top on it.

high_descs: Walk forward past the end of the bed turn right walk towards the side table
Pick up the cell phone on the side table
Turn left then walk forward, then left facing the front of the bed
Put the cell phone on the bed
Turn left then head back to the side table, go to the left side of it
Pick up the cell phone
Turn right then head back to the front of the bed
Put the cell phone beside the other
anns.task_desc: Put two cell phone on the bed
